---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="关于">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold">关于 Qomicex Launcher</h1>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
      <p>Qomicex Launcher 是一个开源的现代化 Minecraft 启动器，基于 Tauri 2 + React 构建，致力于提供流畅、稳定、功能丰富的游戏启动体验。</p>
      <p>项目完全开源，采用 GPL-3.0 协议。我们欢迎社区贡献代码、提交反馈和建议。</p>
      <p>你可以通过以下渠道联系我们：</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">GitHub</span> <a href="https://github.com/Qomicex-Public" class="text-primary underline underline-offset-2">github.com/Qomicex-Public</a></li>
        <li><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">QQ 群</span> <a href="https://qm.qq.com/q/rKiwzrkg8w" class="text-primary underline underline-offset-2" target="_blank">623362446</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-5">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold">技术栈</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {['Tauri 2', 'React 19', 'TypeScript', 'Tailwind CSS', 'ASP.NET Core 10', 'Rust'].map(t => (
          <span class="rounded-md border border-border bg-secondary px-2.5 py-1 text-xs text-secondary-foreground">{t}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
